    "helpingUsText": "Hi, if you‚Äôre here it‚Äôs certainly because you feel like you could help us in some way, either you‚Äôre a translator, or a webdesigner, heck even a programmer. But there are many more ways to contribute. Notably reading the comics and reporting bugs. Or even, the filthiest one of all ! Posting memes in the discord. We would be glad to welcome you there. This is yet another TF2 community project, and if you‚Äôre here, you certainly are part of the community ! So you‚Äôre part of us in a way ! We accept every applications for any sets of skills, but we won‚Äôt accept too much translators per languages, as you know, too many cooks spoil the broth, and such supper, should be exquisite.",
